data.description: Ideal Location! The first house ever built in this well-maintained, highly desired development. As you come up the road you'll see amazing mountain views, slow speed limits, and a perfect cul-de-sac to enjoy an evening walk or bike ride. This ranch has been loved by one family, the original owners- for many years and has endless potential.  The largest lot in the area, almost 5 ACRES!! Enjoy the woods or play some yard games in the nicely leveled yard. In the summer, relax by the inground pool with a brand new liner.  With three bedrooms, two baths, a kitchen, dining room, and living room you'll surely want to turn this house into your own home. No stairs, making grocery unloading a breeze.  There are beautiful hardwood floors along with a stunning fireplace, bring your vision! Only approx. an hour drive to NYC with many mass transit options nearby.
